# Python — repo root ships catalog/data/docs only; tooling stays local.
# Temporary one-shot migration/validation helpers conventionally start with _
# (e.g. _seed_compositions.py, _validate.py) and stay local-only by this rule.
# Exception: scripts under .github/scripts/ are CI infrastructure and tracked.
*.py
!.github/scripts/*.py
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/
.pytest_cache/

